{"tid":225181,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我條cat5 cable 可以去到呢個速度","createTime":"2017-05-01T15:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T19:36:20.000Z","uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"12250479f52882055dc9ed63453245a67d145e68","tid":225181,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.speedtest.net/result/6262501230.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.speedtest.net%2Fresult%2F6262501230.png&h=1b9a03d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCat5 去 router 經 cat5e 去 電腦<br />\n<br />\ncat5唔係去到100 ja咩?"},{"pid":"92b44ebba941931ee16e3315f6f4ceaddf2b9d1d","tid":225181,"uid":17835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://www.speedtest.net/result/6262501230.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.speedtest.net%2Fresult%2F6262501230.png&h=1b9a03d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCat5 去 router 經 cat5e 去 電腦<br />\n<br />\ncat5唔係去到100 ja咩?</blockquote><br />\nCategory 5 cabling, also known as Cat5, is an older type of network cabling. Cat5 cables were made to support theoretical speeds of 10Mbps and 100Mbps. You may be able to get gigabit speeds on a Cat5 cable, particularly if the cable is shorter, but it isn't always guaranteed."},{"pid":"dca95d2b927bf9f14b5c005e32a0fe9fedd73759","tid":225181,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:26:10.000Z","msg":"4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps"},{"pid":"b26c3700e3dd9cdc3f974fb228da1bf83d9a7460","tid":225181,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:32:56.000Z","msg":"你短又無干擾，你拉幾條電線駁埋都一樣行到1000<br />\n<br />\n你得一兩米線又無其他電線拍埋一齊，用Cat6 同cat 5e無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8066a227cde6373decdf93dde3788925302f00c8","tid":225181,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:34:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps</blockquote><br />\n痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a23a3647258589dfc2b848f9de0a81f84fed1e","tid":225181,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps</blockquote><br />\n痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴乜鳩線<br />\ncat 5e 8芯的確行到1000mbps<br />\n樓主由牆入router個條應該唔係cat5線"},{"pid":"92ce8e931da1311e4b2e47c37e3ac4b8546b5046","tid":225181,"uid":31178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:19:29.000Z","msg":"一係100一係1000的，5e可以1000"},{"pid":"13e081b82586156be3125829318f768a8610f0af","tid":225181,"uid":41901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"Cat5 8芯 可以係短距離內做到1000mb"},{"pid":"2c81939a6bd0d370dcb79e9ff1affddd55d25731","tid":225181,"uid":12447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T23:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps</blockquote><br />\n痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴乜鳩線<br />\ncat 5e 8芯的確行到1000mbps<br />\n樓主由牆入router個條應該唔係cat5線</blockquote><br />\n係cat5 <br />\n因為hkbn個條轉左分插做電話加上網<br />\n我又得返1條5e同5<br />\n電腦要5e先認到giga lan<br />\n咁唯有入router用住cat5<br />\n聽日先買多條<br />\n點知再check下 就有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db60a39092687fdee328a891bcd04f88173bfc47","tid":225181,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps</blockquote><br />\n痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴乜鳩線<br />\ncat 5e 8芯的確行到1000mbps<br />\n樓主由牆入router個條應該唔係cat5線</blockquote><br />\n4芯得100m"},{"pid":"48136df061ea014eafa4705ae3a68e365a9fafd6","tid":225181,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T19:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>4芯上到500mbps好似係<br />\n8芯上到1000mbps</blockquote><br />\n痴鳩線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴乜鳩線<br />\ncat 5e 8芯的確行到1000mbps<br />\n樓主由牆入router個條應該唔係cat5線</blockquote><br />\n4芯得100m</blockquote><br />\n我知我好可能記錯4芯 所以戴左頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}